dlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alejandro López-Ortiz (page does not exist)\">Alejandro López-Ortiz</a>, 1993</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://cs.uwaterloo.ca/40th/Chronology/ChronologyGlossary.pdf\">Waterloo@50</a> (pdf) 2007</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Waterloo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_%26_Ophelia_Lazaridis_Quantum-Nano_Centre\">Mike &amp; Ophelia Lazaridis Quantum-Nano Centre</a> at the University of Waterloo, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Mike-and-Ophelia-Lazaridis-Quantum-Nano-Centre.png\">Image</a> by Shipandreceive, August 13, 2012, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.en\">CC BY-SA 3.0</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Waterloo\">University of Waterloo from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228101450\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.076 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.605 s